      "type": "text",
      "id": "extended_notes_body",
      "x": 95,
      "y": 5145,
      "width": 1375,
      "height": 71.5,
      "text": "Build-time work owns remote access, topology discovery, compilation, chunking, and durable indexes.\nRuntime retrieval stays local: classify intent, infer scope, gather candidates, and rank with authority/locality/freshness/evidence signals.\nThe result is a token-budgeted context packet with provenance, omissions, warnings, and ambiguity notes.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Build-time work owns remote access, topology discovery, compilation, chunking, and durable indexes.\nRuntime retrieval stays local: classify intent, infer scope, gather candidates, and rank with authority/locality/freshness/evidence signals.\nThe result is a token-budgeted context packet with provenance, omissions, warnings, and ambiguity notes.",
